    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:45.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# Swarm Feed Topic Naming Convention\n\nAll Powerhouse Swarm feeds follow the `ph:v2:<category>:<scope>` naming pattern.\n\n## Single-user feed topics\n\n- `ph:v2:user:<address>` \u2014 user's drive index\n- `ph:v2:drive:<driveId>` \u2014 drive's document list + folders\n- `ph:v2:doc:<docId>` \u2014 document's operation batch list\n- `ph:v2:profile:<address>` \u2014 public profile (unencrypted)\n- `ph:v2:share:<from>:<to>` \u2014 share manifest between users\n\n## Collaboration feed topics\n\n- `ph:v2:collab:<docId>` \u2014 collaboration index (who's in)\n- `ph:v2:ops:<address>:<docId>` \u2014 per-user operation stream\n\n## Pattern rules\n\n- Every feed has exactly one owner writing, anyone can read\n- Collaboration is modeled as N users, each with their own ops feed\n- The collab index feed tells everyone where to look\n- `v2` indicates schema version (future-proofing)\n",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:45.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:45.000Z"
    }
  },
